---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Andy Hay — UX Research Executive bridging engineering innovation with user understanding.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 py-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-6">
      <img
        src="/images/andy-headshot.jpg"
        alt="Andy Hay"
        class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-accent shrink-0"
      />
      <div>
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.75em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent">// about</span>
        <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.2em] font-bold">Andy Hay</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
          UX Research Executive &middot; Mercer Island, WA
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
      <p class="text-xl text-surface-700 dark:text-surface-300">
        Hi, I'm Andrew (Andy) Hay. I'm a tech enthusiast who followed a path to Human-Computer Interaction (HCI) because I've always wanted to live in "tomorrow's world" today by helping cutting-edge technology improve our lives.
      </p>

      <p>
        I spent 6 years at <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Microsoft</strong> and 17 years co-founding and running <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">User Research International</strong>. Most of that time was spent in enterprise platform environments — places where the right research strategy cuts years of technical and design debt.
      </p>

      <div class="border-l-3 border-l-accent bg-surface-50 p-5 dark:bg-surface-900">
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent">// uri</span>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Scaled <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">User Research International</strong> from 2 to 100+ people. Built specialized teams that served 7 of the world's 10 largest tech companies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        The work ranged from foundational research for <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Microsoft Azure</strong> before it launched, to benchmarking <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Google Cloud Platform</strong>, to pioneering AR/VR research methodologies for <strong class="text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Meta Reality Labs</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Now I'm building. AI agents, automation tools, and the kind of products I spent two decades evaluating for other people. The research instincts are the same. The medium is different.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.65em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent">// </span>Experience
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-8">
        <div class="border-l-3 border-l-accent pl-5">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium text-surface-400">Jan 2025 — Present</span>
          <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Executive Board Member</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">User Research International</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
            Transitioned to board role in January 2025 after 17 years as co-founder and managing partner.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-3 border-l-accent pl-5">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium text-surface-400">Apr 2008 — Jan 2025</span>
          <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Co-Founder & Managing Partner</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">User Research International</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
            Scaled from 2 to 100+ members. Led foundational research for Google Cloud Platform ($50B+ annual revenue), pioneered AR/VR research for Meta Reality Labs, and instituted Go/No-Go usability policies across Microsoft Azure. Built five greenfield teams spanning Cloud Research, Quantitative Research, and AR/VR Labs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-3 border-l-pink pl-5">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium text-surface-400">Jan 2025 — Present</span>
          <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Strategic Advisor</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-pink">Zila Tech Limited</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
            Pro bono strategic advisory for Google Education Partner empowering schools and businesses in Kenya through Google Workspace for Education and Chromebook deployments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-3 border-l-surface-300 dark:border-l-surface-700 pl-5">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium text-surface-400">Jan 2002 — Apr 2008</span>
          <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">UX Research Lead</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Microsoft</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
            Led UX research for Microsoft.com (3rd most visited site globally). Received Gold Star award for System Center Essentials contributions. Developed server division customer model with 29 personas and 1,000+ workflows. Patent awarded for Windows Server Update Services research.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-3 border-l-surface-300 dark:border-l-surface-700 pl-5">
          <span class="font-mono text-[0.7em] font-medium text-surface-400">2000 — 2001</span>
          <h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">Information Architect &middot; Intern</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Oyster Partners &middot; HP Labs</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">
            Awarded patent for trustworthy computing research at HP Labs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Education -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.65em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-pink">// </span>Education
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">MSc Ergonomics & HCI</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">UCL (University College London)</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-surface-800 dark:text-surface-100">BSc Psychology</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Goldsmiths, University of London</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-surface-500 dark:text-surface-400">Specialized in Multivariate Statistics and Experimental Design</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Top Skills -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.65em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent">// </span>Skills
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {[
          'Enterprise AI/ML UX Research',
          'Cloud Platform Research',
          'User Experience Research',
          'Cross-functional Leadership',
          'Voice of the Customer',
          'Data Science',
          'Product Strategy',
          'Contextual Inquiry',
        ].map(skill => (
          <span class="border border-accent/30 px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[0.75em] font-medium text-accent">
            {skill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Connect -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">
        <span class="font-mono text-[0.65em] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-pink">// </span>Connect
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrewcdhay/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-surface-500 hover:text-accent dark:text-surface-400 dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
          </svg>
          linkedin.com/in/andrewcdhay
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/convallyd"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-surface-500 hover:text-accent dark:text-surface-400 dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          github.com/convallyd
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
